Templates&Sketches for AVR µC Series

Copyright (c) 2011 invertednothing.
http://invertednothing.com/

If you are using this don't forget to setup the ARDUINO & AVRDUDE_DIR 
variables in the provided Makefiles!


Using the following libraries
Arduino – http://arduino.cc/ (c abstractions for the avr standard lib)
Arduino-Tiny – http://code.google.com/p/arduino-tiny/ (Arduino libs for ATTiny)

Working with MacOs I'm using the following Open Source Toolchain
avrgcc, avrdude – http://www.obdev.at/products/crosspack/index.html

AVR Fuse Tools
fuse calculator – http://www.engbedded.com/fusecalc/
AVRfuses – http://www.vonnieda.org/software/avrfuses

AVRISP mkII programmer
http://www.atmel.com/dyn/products/tools_card.asp?tool_id=3808

AVR related blogs
http://www.avrfreaks.net/



